text.section:
Each consumer member of the Board:
Shall be a member of the general public;
May not be or ever have been a podiatrist or in training to become a podiatrist;
May not have a household member who is a podiatrist or in training to become a podiatrist;
May not participate or ever have participated in a commercial or professional field related to podiatry;
May not have a household member who participates in a commercial or professional field related to podiatry; and
May not have had within 2 years before appointment a substantial financial interest in a person regulated by the Board.
